00:36:21.520 --> 00:36:22.770
what we can do as individuals.

00:36:22.770 --> 00:36:24.890
And I wondered if
you had top tips,

00:36:24.890 --> 00:36:27.990
when you were talking to either
teams or even organizations,

00:36:27.990 --> 00:36:31.107
